0.000Z","msg":"兩年前 <br />\n鐘意左個又靚又有錢既女神 <br />\n仲靚過model <br />\n但我就只係一個咩都冇既毒拎 <br />\n經過千辛萬苦既努力之後 <br />\n終於同佢傾到計 <br />\n發現左佢唔會歧視毒拎,心地好好 <br />\n我地開始日日吹水 <br />\n我地日日一齊打wow,睇戲果d <br />\n我愈黎愈鐘意佢 <br />\n我地亦都愈行愈埋 <br />\n我地基本上日日由朝玩到晚 <br />\n一生最happy既時間 <br />\n3個月後我搬左去澳洲 <br />\n我地仲會日日吹水 <br />\n過多半年佢病左 <br />\n發現係白血病 <br />\n我知道左之後喊左幾日 <br />\n之後我都仲會同佢吹水 仲係好鐘意佢 <br />\n佢平時最鐘意同我打wow <br />\n有一日佢比左隻寵我 <br />\n&quot;你唔係最鐘意隻雞咩,做咩送比我?&quot; <br />\n&quot;因為我覺得佢會鐘意你多d&quot; <br />\n咁好啦,多謝 <br />\n過多一個月後佢死左 <br />\n我毒左係屋企咩都冇做個幾月 <br />\n冇野做開返wow黎玩 <br />\n見到封mail <br />\n&quot;我愛你&quot; <br />\n之後幾日我喊到返唔到學 <br />\n<br />\n我宜家日日都用佢隻寵係wow周圍行 <br />\n<br />\n我唔知咩係愛,但如果我曾經愛過一個人,果個就係佢"},{"pid":"307f37d726635e8694ec220f5e8718b974d8ca17","tid":481314,"uid":42169,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"不能只有我看到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca154664d34a8e573315703209fe904cf82e3cb3","tid":481314,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"兩單都有啲熟面口，hall 雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203d7eb9c25d45e80362c52af12de8fe67b54a10","tid":481314,"uid":42169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742bdfad4006e42fbd12a2312505d43fc84a748e","tid":481314,"uid":42169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52215e7dff8af005b15f5c06501f6b8e0e5d088","tid":481