佢qooza?ac 我login左入去睇<br />\n原來佢由識我個日到佢生日個日都有keep住寫 每篇都會有相 而且篇篇都有lock pw <br />\n我一路睇一路喊 係佢最後個一篇diary(即係8月22號) <br />\n寫左好多對我?感受 叮囑我有咩壞習慣要改 仲有好多係連我自己都唔發覺?野<br />\n最後佢寫 我曾經想係走之前霸住你一日 攬住你訓 早過你起身睇你個睡相 整早餐你食 睇住你打機 kiu住你手臂去行下街 嗲下你買公仔比我 扮下小女人 夜晚去食pizza 送我返屋企前比一個goodbye kiss你 但係我做唔到 我怕我唔捨得你 更加怕你會憎我太自私 所以我只希望可以係你心中佔一小撮位置 唔求你無時無刻都記得我 但求你唔好忘記我 最後希望另一個平行時空?我地可以係埋一齊 不會再見了 mr.right</blockquote><br />\nwa屌，又睇左次，好自虐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d750bd4030893cf58adb1044992f7c084743d0f4","tid":481314,"uid":42169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792bb15524ffb8a645ae0457e33d928ea0bb6304","tid":481314,"uid":42169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ef710e2ee6a5061d005b0b7e9db571d7acfdb","tid":481314,"uid":42169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"今晚再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30029cc89ff52733259a622677fe8e3bd1b96ce","tid":481314,"uid":118642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post痴線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個心係咁比野打咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec65ce9cc970d7cfef5ff1b46dd55ad3d9164f90","tid":481314,"uid":36558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"讓晚風輕輕吹送了落霞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr